  Hit-hang7 kau-chhiang5 koh toa7-han3, the2-keh ho2, koh u7 lat8, chiu7 chin iaN5--lang5. Tui3 hit si5 Eng2-hok-ah chiu7 kap A-thiam-peh cho3-hoe2 tiam3. Eng2-hok-ah ko2-chin chin kut-lat8, tiaN5-thau5 tiaN5-boe2 cheng2-li2 kau3 chin chheng-khi3, chhu3-cheng5 au7-piah e5 li5-pa long2 koh teng5 ui5, ti-tiau5, ke-tiau5 long2 koh teng5 cheng2-li2; m7-na7 an2-ni, si3-ke3 chit8-khang chit8-khut e5 sou2-chai7 long2 thun7 hou7 i piN5. Chit-e5 ke hut-jian5 chhin-chhiuN7 tit-tioh8 sin e5 oah8-khi3, na2-chun2 chhiu7-bak8 chiap-tioh8 chhun-thiN e5 un-loan2, long2 koh puh-iN2 e5 khoan2-sit. Koe3-khi3 A-thiam-peh ni5-lau7 lah, chu7-jian5 tak8 hang7 u7 pang3 khah bo5 chiu-chi3, lam7-lam7 lui3-lui3. TaN ke-lai7 na2-chun2 u7 sin e5 chu2-lang5 lai5 chiang2-li2 e5 khoan2-sit, tak8 hang7 to u7 sin e5 khi3-siong7. 
  Na7-si7 A-thiam-peh choe3 su7 bo5 bong2-tong2, bo5 ham5-hou5, i long2 bo5 kong2 sim2-mih8. I chu3-sin5 tiam7-tiam7 teh khoaN3 chit-e5 chheng-lian5. Te7 it, ai3 khoaN3 i e5 sin3-giong2, u7 hoaN-hi2 chiap-siu7 Ia5-sou a2-bo5? Phin2-heng7 u7 teng5-thau5-siN a2-bo5? Te7 ji7, ai3 khoaN3 chit-e5 chheng-lian5 e5 sim-seng3 u7 tiaN7 a2-bo5, chin-sim beh cho3-hoe2 tiam3 a2-bo5? Ban7-ban7 koan-chhat i e5 heng5-tong7 ku2-chi2, kong2-oe7, sim-su chaiN2-iuN7? Chhan5, hng5, soaN-phiaN5, chhu3, sui-jian5 si7 bo5 che7, m7-ku2 si7 choan5 chai5-san2, si7 chit8 ke kho3 chiah-e5 lai5 seng-oah8--e5. Lai7-bin7 bo5 pat8-lang5, chi2-u7 Chhiu-kui3 ah, na7 e7 eng7-tit, chiu7 chiong Chhiu-kui3-ah phoe3--i, chu7 an2-ni chio jip8--lai5, ia7 choe3 beng5-leng5-chu2 e5 khoan2-sit. Te7 saN, na7 beh an2-ni, tioh8 chhun5 Chhiu-kui3-ah e5 i3-su3, chim-chiok khoaN3 in nng7 e5 chheng-lian5 e7 hah8 a2 be7? Nng7 e5 u7 ian5-hun7 a2-bo5? Sou2-i2 A-thiam-peh tiam7-tiam7 long2 m7 kong2. Khi2-thau5 si7 kong2 choe3 tng5-kang, chiah8 pian7-pian7 chit8 goeh8-jit8 30 khou, koh khi3 chiah chiau3 khoaN3. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni chit8 ni5 lian5 ku2, lai5 e5 si5 Eng2-kok-ah si7 21 hoe3 e5 oa2 chiaN5 chap8 goeh8-a2 hit si5, taN bak8-chit8-nih si7 keh-ni5 e5 oa2 11 goeh8 lah. Chit si5 Eng2-hok-ah si7 22 hoe3, Chhiu-kui3-ah si7 21 hoe3. A-thiam-m2 tiaN7 koaN2 A-thiam-peh, ka7 i kong2, ¡§Lau7-e3, khoaN3 si7 tho3-tong3 lah. To hou7 lan2 khoaN3 ni5-goa7 ku2 lah, khoaN3 liau2 seng3-cheng5 to chin ho2, ia7 chin kut-lat8.¡¨ A-thiam-peh sim-lai7 iau2 teh tan2 chit8 hang7 su7, chiu7 kong2, ¡§Ban7-chiah leh, goa2 iau2 teh tan2 chit8 hang7 su7, na7-si7 goa2 m7 kong2-chhut, beh tan2 kau3 kau3 si5 chiah lai5 phah-sng3.¡¨ 
  A-thiam-m2 liah8-chun2 si7 hou7 in kap-pang5 hit jit8 ai3 ki2-heng5 kiat-hun-sek, ai3 chhiaN2 lang5-kheh tioh8 thai5-ti. Sou2-i2 i chiu7 in3 kong2, ¡§Lau7-e3, goa2 u7 chhun5-pan7 leh la3, li2 ia7 soa3 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 goa2 u7 keng chit8 chiah pah chhit-peh kin e5 ti-phoe, koh ke, go5, ah chit8 tin7, li2 kiam2 bo5 khoaN3-tioh8.¡¨ ¡¨M7-si7 hit ho7 su7 lah.¡¨ A-thiam-m2 sahN-thau5 m7 khi2, soa3 tiam7-tiam7 m7-kaN2 koh mng7. A-thiam-peh ia7 chu7 an2-ni tiam7-tiam7. 
  Chap8-it goeh8-boe2 u7 chit8 le2-pai3, bok8-su hoat-piau2 kong2 chiok Seng3-tan3 cheng5 beh mng7 to7-li2, na7 kam-goan7 chiap-siu7 se2-le2, beh koat-sim jin7 Chu2 lai5 kui-oa2 I e5 lang5, thang lai5 po3-mia5. Chu7 cha2 Eng2-hok chiu7 chin pi7-pan7 sim, peh8-oe7-ji7 Seng3-si, Seng3-keng ia7 long2 chin sek8, e7 hiau2 thak8 lah. Chin-chiaN3 u7 koat-sim beh chiap-siu7 Chu2 e5 kiu3-in, sou2-i2 i chiu7 kap A-thiam-peh chham-siong5, kong2 i beh khi3 po3-mia5 mng7 to7-li2, kho2-i2 put kho2-i2. A-thiam-peh kong2 chu7-jian5 kho2-i2, chong2-si7 iu5 li2 e5 chu7-iu5, m7-thang chhut ti7 bian2-kiong2, koh-khah m7-thang chham-chhap pat8-mih8 i3-su3. Nia2 se2-le2, chi2-u7 chiu7-si7 hian2-beng5 li2 u7 goan7-i3 hoan2-hoe2 chiap-siu7 Ia5-sou choe3 li2 e5 Chu2, chi2-u7 an2-ni e5 i3-su3, i2-goa7 m7-thang siuN7 kong2 nia2 se2-le2 kap li2 tiam3 goa2 chia a2-si7 bo5 tiam3 goa2 chia u7 sim2-mih8 koan-he7. 
